Bit more @diorbeauty on the feed today. The two new blushes in Rosewood. I do like the powder, but the cream blush is definitely my favourite.
Which do you prefer?

I’ve always had quite oily skin, and although I reach for a heavier moisturiser in the winter months, I tend to find my skin can’t cope if they’re too thick. @skinrocks new addition to their range is the light moisturiser. The texture is very light and watery, it feels incredibly refreshing and hydrates my skin like a dream! Another winner from @skinrocks ❤️

Gifted

#skinrocks #oilyskin #over40sskincare

Despite my bad reaction to the new @diorbeauty lip balms, I still love this brand, and although I can’t use them, they can just look pretty on my feed ❤️
I have to add that I contacted Dior and they want to call me to discuss. I’ll let you know how I get on!

#diorlove #diorflatlay #luxurymakeup

latestPosts.caption:
@pixibeauty are killing it with their new launches and it these are one of my favourites! These new lip masks are beyond cute, with sleek design and handy applicator, but they are so hydrating and thick and love the shades too ❤️

#pixipmasks #lipobsession #softlips💋

Ok let’s just start by saying, I love @diorbeauty products. These new balm tints are super juicy and feel lovely on the lips. HOWEVER, my lips did not agree! I had a terrible reaction. My lips came out in blisters and were sore and swollen. After they calmed down, my lips shedded like a snake.
It’s a sad, HUGE pass from me.
Anyone else have a reaction?
Always a sucker for a cream blush! Trying out these two beautiful shades from @codebeautiful . Which is your favourite shade?

I’m really enjoying the peel off stains atm, and this newbie from @makeuprevolution is just perfect for the Summer and so affordable!
I like to pair it with a nude lipliner and a touch of clear gloss and I’m good to go! The colour last all day, it doesn’t budge!
Do you like these peel off formulas?

Current blushes on rotation. I think the absolute winner from these is the @westmanatelier and the @yslbeauty blush.

So I finally gave in and bought a few bits from the new @diorbeauty collection. So, let’s start with the winner, this gorgeous warm toned pallet. Every shade perfection. I absolutely love every colour.
Unfortunately, not all my new purchases were hits, more to come!

#diornewcollection #diorpallet #luxurybeauty #bougiemakeup

So when I received this peel off lipliner from @makeuprevolution I didn’t really have high hopes, it looked a bit of a gimmick. However, I was very pleasantly surprised. It takes a bit of practice, but it leaves a lovely lip liner stain that lasts all day. My daughter keeps stealing this from me, so I know it’s a hit with her too!

Gifted
